<![CDATA[<font face="arial" style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><span style="font-size: 12pt;">Hi&nbsp;{!Contact.FirstName},</span></font><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">As an NCS graduate who attended one of our employability workshops with Lloyds Banking Group and Business in the Community (BITC), we have an <b>amazing opportunity</b> for you!</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt; text-align: center;"><img src="http://www.mentorsme.co.uk/images/uploads2/BITC-logo.jpg"></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">BITC helped us organise the workshops through their <b><a href="http://www.bitc.org.uk/programmes/business-connectors">Business Connectors</a></b> scheme, and now they're looking for one young person to speak to a group of high profile figures about their experience at the sessions.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">You'll need to be comfortable speaking for a couple of minutes in front of people like <b>Rob Wilson MP</b> (Minister for Civil Society) and executives from companies including <b>John Lewis</b>, <b>Fujitsu</b>, <b>Lloyds Banking Group</b> and <b>Carillion</b>.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">It's an amazing opportunity to meet some highly influential people in the world of business and government, and take part in some high profile networking. You will be accompanied by a member of staff from The Challenge.</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b>The event details are as follows:</b></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><ul><li><font face="arial"><b>Date: </b>Wednesday 27th April</font></li><li><font face="arial"><b>Time: </b>09:30 - 11:30</font></li><li><font face="arial"><b>Location: </b>Bethnal Green (exact venue TBC)</font></li></ul><div><font face="arial">There is only <b>ONE</b> space for an NCS graduate to speak, so if you are interested, please fill out <b><a href="https://docs.google.com/forms/d/1QohlBL1o0pQyD515qoJNwcAJN2rvpK0xXEsZxqQ4PrA/viewform">this short application form</a>&nbsp;by 09:00 on Thursday 21st April</b>. If you are successful, we will be in touch to confirm details.</font></div></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><br></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b><i>As the event is taking place during a school day, The Challenge Society can provide a letter of proof for your school to excuse your absence.</i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><font face="arial"><b><i><br></i></b></font></div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;">Kind regards,</div><div style="color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><br></div><div style="font-family: arial; font-size: 12pt;"><b><font color="#ff0000">The Challenge Society</font></b></div><div><font face="arial" color="#ff0000"><b>http://tcsnorthlondon.co.uk</b></font></div>]]></td>
